  "title": "(Talk to patients) 1 Year Temp Healthier SG Ambassador @ WEST [$12/h!] #HJCT",
  "description": "<p>Salary: $12/hour</p><p>Working Hours: 5 days a week</p><p>Mon-Fri, 8am - 430pm</p><p>Sometimes will be activated 1 day on weekends </p><p> Job Responsibilities</p><p>• Assist with HSG assisted enrolment through small group sharing and one-to-one engagement with patients/residents in outreach settings such as hospitals, designated booths or community settings, via the mobile app or system application.</p><p>• Explain to patients the benefits of HSG initiatives and the importance to enrol, make the first visit to review Health Plan with the Primary Care Provider, fulfil the preventive health recommendations and follow up for review annually.</p><p>• Attend to HSG related enquiries from patients and caregivers.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>• Proficient in Microsoft Applications.</p><p>• Comfortable with the use of technology (e.g. mobile app and systems applications).</p><p>• Able to tolerate standing for 3-4 hours minimally throughout the day.</p><p><br /><br />TELE me at @stefanielohwm or WA me at https://wa.me/+6591728493 NOW!</p><p>Interested candidates please submit your resume to healthcare12@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Jace Choo Oi Kei</p><p>Personnel EA License No.: R1875164</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA Licence No.: 99C4599) </p>",
